## v3.17 - Verify that an active session list is displayed in the account profile or similar of each user. The user should be able to terminate any active session.

### Why is this required?

If a malicious user is attempting to hijack a session, this information would appear in the session list and a legitimate user would be alerted to the fact.

### Applicability (Level 1)

This objective applies to all apps that handle sessions.

### Guidelines for developers

Ensure that the active session list is easy for a user to find.
